                <td bgcolor="#e9e9e9" valign="top"><font color="#000000" face="arial" size="2"><small>Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;06/18/2003&nbsp;: 06:39:55 AM</small><hr size="2"><span class="spnMessageText"> Fascinating.  People should take notice.  While SWG doesn't seem to be EQ-related ...they say SWG, I see EQ2.  If you think for a moment that some of these issues (the 'mission' system, the merchant system, the combat system, etc) won't be the exact same thing in EQ2, you are kidding yourself.</span></font></td>
